@startuml
[*] --> Idle : view time
Idle --> AdjustingTime : adjust time
AdjustingTime --> ChangingHour : change hour
ChangingHour --> HourIncreased : increase hour
HourIncreased --> Idle : done
AdjustingTime --> ChangingMinute : change minute
ChangingMinute --> MinuteIncreased : increase minute
MinuteIncreased --> Idle : done
AdjustingTime --> AlarmSetting : set alarm
AlarmSetting --> AlarmOn : turn on alarm
AlarmOn --> Idle : done
AlarmSetting --> AlarmOff : turn off alarm
AlarmOff --> Idle : done
Idle --> AlarmTriggered : current time matches alarm
AlarmTriggered --> Ringing : ring alarm
Ringing --> Idle : stop ringing
Idle --> LightOn : toggle light
LightOn --> LightOff : release button
@enduml
